msgstr "En línea"

#: Settings/Service/PaymentRequirement.php:27
msgid ""
"Customers are required to make an online payment. If no payment is made "
"within the specified pending time, the reservation will be automatically "
"cancelled."
msgstr ""
"Los clientes deben pagar en línea. Si no se realiza ningún pago dentro del "
"tiempo máximo pendiente, la reserva se cancela automáticamente."

#: Settings/Service/PaymentRequirement.php:29
