msgid "Participate"
msgstr "Participar"

#: Settings/Service/Personal_Participate.php:21
msgid ""
"Turn this off if you want to exclude your availability events from being "
"counted for this service. This can be useful for temporary needs, such as "
"vacations, as it allows you to maintain your availability schedule unchanged."
msgstr ""
"Desactiva esto si quieres evitar que los eventos de tu disponibilidad se "
"cuenten para este servicio. Es útil como necesidad temporal, por ejemplo, "
